Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝我什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頸部、後腦、從右眼到嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右上臂、右下臂、無名指、左臂、手肘、拇指、中指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從肋骨部分到心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部到腹部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右胯、右腿、左腿、左腳指頭全部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在一瞬間就把我解體成了17塊肉塊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞  搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  原來是有彥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嚇我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話應該是我說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉看起來不像沒事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被一個奇怪的傢伙追
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去告訴老師比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近不太平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該去通知警察才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓塚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是我想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我解體成了17塊肉塊  不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要「復仇」咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野  你慌張什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的複習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.60,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：「復仇」音同「複習」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐籐  你來回答看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野  你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不太對勁喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說家裡發生了什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是住不習慣老家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累積了太多壓力？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓力嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以加入你們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野  你到底是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙今天好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel學姊你有在玩角色扮演嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有那種興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓塚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天晚上我要跟父母到餐廳吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間旅館的義大利餐廳很有名喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  遠野也真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟已經離開家八年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像是別人的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事太好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當聽你說要搬家的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你會轉學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是初二那年冬天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初二？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在裡面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門被鎖上出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候救了我的人是遠野沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我心裡這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在緊急時刻會來救我的一定是像遠野這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的人是什麼樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是平常老是發呆的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我一直相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我又遇到危險  遠野你一定會來救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是那麼可靠的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛說了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來得還真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你等得好累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來得還真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你等得好累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到終點了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了人之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該用這種口氣說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我原諒你也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已經復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復  復活？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不是人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子沒時間詳細說明了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的使魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你造成的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別管這個了  我們得快點離開這裡才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間大概已經被找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不找個安全的地方可就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以在這裡殺了你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴少爺好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽志貴少爺說過什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴少爺四點多曾經回來過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來跟一個女孩子出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看起來只是個普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你不是人類到底是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不喜歡這個稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說我是吸血鬼是不是比較容易理解？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活？ 吸血鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種鬼話我怎麼可能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  應該已經被你殺死的我為何還能站在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嗎  我根本沒有殺你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰？ 竟然能殺死我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個普通的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生還真是厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你當我的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盾牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為你才受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在還沒好之前如果被襲擊的話不是很危險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被襲擊？ 被誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不就是吸血鬼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道最近這個城市所發生的事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說連續離奇兇殺案嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在找我的那傢伙幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說  除了你之外還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我當盾牌該不會是要我跟那傢伙打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少無理取鬧了  我不可能辦得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個普通的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會殺死你一定也是因為出了什麼差錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次殺普通的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有拒絕的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我才變衰弱的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我預計的還要早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在正在用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須在他吃完餌食之前逃離這裡才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是餌食？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid Brunestud
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Nero嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再靠近過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nero Chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被稱為「渾沌」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渾沌？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽過傳言  不過沒想到他會那麼凶殘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑現在的我沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種怪物絕對不可能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經看到那傢伙的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能讓你活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↓Trailer↓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰慄、悔恨以及決意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺穿咆哮襲擊而來的黑色野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:24:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  真月譚月姬「直死之魔眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得見 線條…
